HEADWORD: exercisable
<hw>ex"er*ci`sa*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>a.</pos> <def>That may be
exercised, used, or exerted; <as>as, the stock options are
<ex>exercisable</ex> for only five years from the date of
issue</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exercise</ent>⟦br⟧
